01:17.350 --> 01:22.390
So you are going to get a response saying, nope, I don't have the context of your 24 due to the cutoff

01:22.390 --> 01:23.680
of the trained data.

01:24.190 --> 01:27.760
That is what you are going to be getting up from the model.

